title: Tideland
description:
Dark and beautiful poetry from a dark and beautiful mind. To paraphrase Gilliam from his introduction - 

Many of you will not like this film. Luckily, many of you will love it. And then there are many of you who will not know what to think when the film finishes but, hopefully, you'll be thinking. 

Additional files include Gilliam's video introduction plus French and English subtitles. Enjoy.
